In this paper we are interested in the Maximum Likelihood Estimator (MLE) of
the vector parameter of an autoregressive process of order $p$ with regular
stationary Gaussian noise. We exhibit the large sample asymptotical properties
of the MLE under very mild conditions. Simulations are done for fractional
Gaussian noise (fGn), autoregressive noise (AR(1)) and moving average noise
(MA(1)).